# DESIGN SPECIFICATION

The JSON above provides a complete design specification for the Product Details screen.  It leverages components from the design system where possible, utilizing fallbacks for missing components, and adheres strictly to the defined design system rules for typography, spacing, and color.  The three-container architecture is implemented for optimal mobile experience. The `appbar` component displays a back navigation icon and a concise title and the  `bottom navigation` component is included, providing standard app navigation.  The main content area contains detailed product information.
```

